column2: IMAGES Images of empty streets in Kyiv following an overnight assault by the Russian forces. Ukrainian soldiers repulsed a Russian attack in the capital, the military said early Saturday, as a defiant President Volodymyr Zelensky vowed his pro-Western country would not be bowed by Moscow.
